scene.message:
Student: {ctl0f:1}! The place{nl}
across from the library's{nl}
become a casino!!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm raking it in! You should{nl}
go check it out too!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: While you guys were{nl}
gone, I sank all the club{nl}
funds into poker...{waitkey}{clearbox}The next guy to play's gonna{nl}
be lucky. The jackpot bonus{nl}
must be sky-high by now...{waitkey}{ret}

Junior: Hee hee hee. It's all{nl}
over now.{waitkey}{clearbox}We're all going to die someday{nl}
anyway... this just moves it{nl}
up a little. Yes,{wait_fr:30} that's all.{waitkey}{clearbox}We get to end our lives still{nl}
beautiful, so we ought to{nl}
thank the Snow Queen.{waitkey}{ret}

Junior: Hee hee hee. In a deep{nl}
blue room, a deep blue piano.{waitkey}{clearbox}Deep blue curtains, and a deep{nl}
blue carpet. What kind of{nl}
room could it be, I wonder?{waitkey}{clearbox}It's the room just to the{nl}
left as you leave here. Hee{nl}
hee hee hee.{waitkey}{ret}

Junior: Hee hee hee. In a{nl}
pitch-dark room, a light{nl}
floats.{waitkey}{clearbox}The light takes me away to{nl}
another world. It's so{nl}
lovely.{waitkey}{clearbox}At the crossroads just outside{nl}
here, turn left and go{nl}
straight on, and there it is.{waitkey}Hee hee hee hee.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Huh, so go off{nl}
fighting for a while and the{nl}
jackpot can climb, huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I'm hungry~ Come to{nl}
think of it, where'd the home{nl}
ec room go?{waitkey}{clearbox}I've got a fair bit of{nl}
leftover baking ingredients{nl}
from this morning, just{nl}
sitting there.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A casino? Get mixed up{nl}
in something like that and{nl}
you'll ruin yourself.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Once in a while I'd{nl}
love to cut loose and hit{nl}
the casino.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: That girl by the{nl}
window... she's been muttering{nl}
something for a while now.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: That girl by the{nl}
window... she's still{nl}
muttering something.{waitkey}{ret}
